title: Daily Wire Backstage: Watch and Wait Edition
description:
Will Hurricane Dorian make U.S. landfall? Which Democrats will be left standing after the third debate? Can America ever fully recover from the Fried Chicken Sandwich War of 2019?
Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Michael Knowles, Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing as they get to the bottom of these questions and more.

Date: 09-04-2019
